<h1>You've been invited to test Launch10!</h1>

<p><strong><%= @admin.name %></strong> has invited you to try Launch10 as part of our friends &amp; family preview.</p>

<% if @credits > 0 %>
  <p>You've been gifted <strong><%= @credits %> credits</strong> to get started.</p>
<% end %>

<p>Click the button below to set up your password and start using Launch10:</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= @reset_url %>" style="background-color: #4F46E5; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block;">
    Set Up Your Account
  </a>
</p>

<p><small>This link will expire in 6 hours. If it expires, ask your inviter to resend.</small></p>
